MOV E INTO THE NORWEGIAN SEA AND INTO SCANDINAVIA ON SUNDAY WITH ANOTHER
RIDGE OF HIGH PRESSURE BLDN ACROSS THE UK FM THE ATLANTIC. STRG WINDS ARE
